{"tid":378222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天鴿襲澳】2長者被捕！涉WeChat謠傳政府瞞停車場5死","createTime":"2017-08-28T10:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T11:16:47.000Z","uid":48093,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b228261d192c4de244fdd07c220db7c3058ca46a","tid":378222,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170828/large/1503914589_26b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170828%2Flarge%2F1503914589_26b6.jpg&h=d2303b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳門司警扣留2名73歲和68歲的兄妹，他們涉嫌在網上發佈不實消息，包括聲稱政府封鎖在筷子基停車場發現5具遺體的消息。司警表示，有人未證實消息真確，就用手機通訊軟件「微信」（WeChat），轉載到至少6個聊天群組、30個私人對話中，涉嫌觸犯侵犯行使公共當局權力之法人罪，將被移送到檢察院。司警又表示，案件仍在調查，不排除有更多人涉案。<br />\n<br />\n司警又呼籲居民，不應轉發未經證實的消息及言論，否則除會引起不必要的猜測及恐慌，亦會觸犯刑事罪行。"},{"pid":"29a63354fc66590d3dc75877b1778581dd95ced4","tid":378222,"uid":81995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:29:06.000Z","msg":"廢老以為自己轉發訊息好威威 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f2ec6aade046070f28b1f1591bd233668d4908","tid":378222,"uid":15323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:29:14.000Z","msg":"就快到香港架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c85e18515eaad6426a99247b91712ef608a52de","tid":378222,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:30:09.000Z","msg":"共產黨is watching you"},{"pid":"5eafc019aee22f3265c70a217f0b326effcdf5a8","tid":378222,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"遲啲班廢中廢老send長輩圖都會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"h